Jonathan, the gentleman, a master of hamon who takes hits like a champ.
Joseph, the trickster, beats his foes with his resourcefulness.
Jotaro, the delinquent, punches his opponents to utter submission.
Josuke, bearer of the greatest hairstyle, turns foes to allies with his strength and healing.
Giorno, the thug, whose resolve gives him strength to accomplish anything.

These are the JoJos from 5 parts, animated for the people to see.
But beyond what is animated, lies the manga for people to read.
One day, that too shall be animated.
